title: Iowa Department of Transportation, Incorporated Cities, Iowa, 2000
name: Iowa Department of Transportation, Incorporated Cities, Iowa, 2000
description:
Abstract:
    This coverage contains polygons that represent the boundaries of the 954 incorporated cities and towns in Iowa. This coverage also has interior boundaries of unincorporated areas within city boundaries. 
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.
